data.description: Charming Bi-Level Home with 3 Bedrooms, 2 Bathrooms, and 3-Car Tandem Garage. Welcome to this inviting bi-level home boasting a perfect blend of comfort and functionality. Situated under the ownership of one caring owner, this residence offers a cozy ambiance and practical amenities. Newer updates include a newer roof, sewer line, electric panel, Anderson windows with built in blinds, and garage doors with power openers. The garage is finished and has a gas heater, furnace, A/C, and central vacuum. The older remodeled kitchen features stainless steel appliances. Bedrooms: 3 spacious bedrooms providing ample space for rest and relaxation. Two bathrooms ensuring convenience for the household. Tandem Garage: A rare find, a 3-car tandem garage offering abundant parking space and storage options. A charming gas fireplace, perfect for cozy evenings and adding warmth to the living space. Enjoy the convenience and practicality of a bi-level layout, separating living and private spaces seamlessly. Lovingly maintained by a single owner, ensuring attention to detail and care in every corner. Enjoy a covered deck off the dining area. The large backyard has a shed for storage and a bonus oversized cedar building with a metal roof that can be used for a Hot Tub and has power, adding versatility to the space. A dog run is available in the backyard with a dog door to the garage. In the front yard, a driveway entrance has been installed into the sidewalk; park a toy here. The property is positioned in close proximity to Webster Elementary, Mesa Ridge High School, and James Madison Charter Academy. It also enjoys a convenient location near Fort Carson and various other military bases, as well as parks and local businesses. Easy access to I-25. This delightful home is a perfect opportunity for those seeking comfort, functionality, and a touch of charm. Don't miss out on making it your own! Contact us today to schedule a viewing.
